OL,3,CSouthport killer's dad hears of
OL,4,C'complete disdain' from victims'
OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,FThe families of the three girls killed
OL,8,Fin the Southport attack have "complete
OL,9,Fdisdain" for the father of their
OL,10,Fmurderer, he has been told.
OL,12,FAlphonse R said he was "desperately
OL,13,Fsorry" for the families of Elsie Dot
OL,14,FStancombe, seven, Bebe King, six, and
OL,15,FAlice da Silva Aguiar, nine, who were
OL,16,Fmurdered by his son Axel Rudakubana on
OL,17,F29 July 2024.
