OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,FBut, as he was questioned by counsel
OL,8,Ffor the bereaved families, Nicholas
OL,9,FBowen KC, at the public inquiry at
OL,10,FLiverpool Town Hall, he was criticised
OL,11,Ffor his responses.
OL,13,FAddressing Alphonse R, Mr Bowen said:
OL,14,F"(The families) want me, all three
OL,15,Fsets of parents - and I'm sorry to
OL,16,Fhave to say this to you publicly and
OL,17,Fharshly.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@BpmvD@Opn
