OL,7,FHe added: "I think the love I had for
OL,8,Fhim overrode good judgment."
OL,10,FAlphonse R appeared to cry at one
OL,11,Fpoint during his evidence when he was
OL,12,Fasked if he had feared AR had gone to
OL,13,Fcarry out an attack after realising he
OL,14,Fhad left their home in Old School
OL,15,FClose, Banks, Lancashire, on the
OL,16,Fmorning.
