OL,3,CSouthport killer's dad hears of
OL,4,C'complete disdain' from victims'
OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,FHe said: "The only hope I was hanging
OL,8,Fon to was that he didn't take
OL,9,Fanything, he didn't take a bag and I
OL,10,Fdidn't imagine that he would carry a
OL,11,Fknife somewhere else.
OL,13,F"I was just clinging onto the hope
OL,14,Fthat he is going for a walk, if he was
OL,15,Fcarrying a bag I would have ran out."
OL,17,FHe said he later learnt from a message
OL,18,Ffrom someone in his church group about
OL,19,Fthe attack.
