OL,3,CSouthport killer's dad hears of
OL,4,C'complete disdain' from victims'
OL,5,Cfamilies
OL,7,FHe said: "I immediately feared that AR
OL,8,Fcould be involved."
OL,10,FHe said he did not have any idea why
OL,11,FAR chose to target innocent young
OL,12,Fgirls at the Taylor Swift-themed dance
OL,13,Fclass.
OL,15,FHe said: "I don't understand how he
OL,16,Fgot there and he chose that place."
OL,18,FThe inquiry is due to hear from AR's
OL,19,Fmother Laetitia Muzayire later on
OL,20,FThursday.
